{"title":"等待雪花","authors":["吴晓民"],"dates":[{"year":1983,"month":1,"day":4}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"等待雪花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吴晓民"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秋天的黄叶在风中散落而去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你在向哪里张望？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把什么等待？在等待什么？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飘飘的白云从蓝天上飞去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你独自向哪里走？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把什么等待？在等待什么？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"等待着最后的一朵鲜花。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让它们都去吧，不必感伤。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那雁群、浮萍、小草和菊花。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我就站在这儿迎接。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把雪花等待，在等待雪花。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我看见了她们俏丽的身姿。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梦里，我轻声地笑过。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"清晨，她们都涌上眉梢。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多么多么久远了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当时我还那么年少。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梦啊，果真都是梦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一年一度，她们准来拜访。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那时，我快活地展臂扑去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"现在，又等到了这个时节，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可我早已不那么年少。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎么办呢？用什么姿态？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还象孩童时那样？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我摇摇头，含蓄地微笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在心中，我系上春天的铃铛。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}